
This directory contains the following sub-directories


  bar/

    the "better-bar" simulation.  An animated ALT demonstrator,
    with added extras.

  game/

    an interactive multi-user text based adventure game.

  robots/

    David Wood's robot demonstrators and Sam's particle demo.

  shootout/

    Implementations in occam-pi of some of the examples from
    <http://shootout.alioth.debian.org/>.

  ttygames/

    A collection of text-based games and other fun things
    written in occam-pi.

